{"tid":843822,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"街拍美照疑修圖　木村光希零加工美腿照反擊","createTime":"2018-10-01T12:18:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T04:20:20.000Z","uid":9573,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1ddafee53edd6082d24a5aa71f97d15099c994bf","tid":843822,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T12:18:36.000Z","msg":"日本女星木村光希，頂著雙親木村拓哉、工藤靜香的光環，剛踏入演藝圈就備受矚目，人氣極高的她更獲邀參加巴黎時裝周，不過卻傳出祕赴比利時，接拍的美照遭指長腿有修圖之嫌，讓她立刻分享零加工美腿照「驗明正身」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-09-27/656/20180927002738.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-09-27%2F656%2F20180927002738.jpg&h=0326cda1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n身材擁有完美比例的木村光希，日前遠赴比利時工作時，順道在當地知名景點拍照留念，卻被眼尖網友抓包腿的比例不合理之外，腿部線條以及後方背景都有歪斜的痕跡，隊友更告訴他：「這就是中國，我們應按照相關意思去做。」質疑她用修圖軟體修過頭了，把腿拉長到不合身體比例。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180829/large/1535542119_54a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180829%2Flarge%2F1535542119_54a0.jpg&h=a17a171a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日她曬出身穿熱褲坐在保母車的照片，不過經網友驗證此次並無「加工」痕跡，照片中也無任何地方變形，證實木村光希的腿可是「真材實料」。"},{"pid":"9b93444f9875daf25df9c1fe0f4eb15e7f6b3e29","tid":843822,"uid":153497,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T12:27:13.000Z","msg":"又話會炒摩佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ab998da944d1661f796d7a6dab076417d75c38","tid":843822,"uid":19437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T12:28:35.000Z","msg":"木村扮女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140da4665c00578397703e3fb2815c283e18fbd5","tid":843822,"uid":162316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T13:41:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">隊友更告訴他：「這就是中國，我們應按照相關意思去做。」</span>"},{"pid":"af2f138a500e9fafae8f81e6aba70e3fcf607864","tid":843822,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T13:44:47.000Z","msg":"蔡思達"},{"pid":"36aa036246670420a6b467c92f20e87c5d6bb821","tid":843822,"uid":157872,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:13:22.000Z","msg":"雖然摩佬就嚟比人炒，但都唔使唔post千雪㗎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6564f64f230d488873704cb79c202e7a688dfe94","tid":843822,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36aa036246670420a6b467c92f20e87c5d6bb821","tid":843822,"uid":157872,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:13:22.000Z","msg":"雖然摩佬就嚟比人炒，但都唔使唔post千雪㗎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T15:07:46.000Z","msg":"應該好臭"},{"pid":"6ee8a78245ff6b31a8b401b5fcec5da222836434","tid":843822,"uid":166062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36aa036246670420a6b467c92f20e87c5d6bb821","tid":843822,"uid":157872,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T14:13:22.000Z","msg":"雖然摩佬就嚟比人炒，但都唔使唔post千雪㗎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T04:20:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}